# Tar Spot Risk Dashboard

This is a web application that predicts the risk of tar spot disease in corn based on 7-day average weather conditions. The app allows users to:

- Select a location via an interactive map
- Automatically fetch weather data for that location
- Manually input field conditions (e.g., irrigation)
- Calculate tar spot risk (Low, Moderate, High)

